Privacy Policy for SalePaste

SalePaste does not collect, store, transmit, or share any personal data or clipboard content. All processing happens locally on your Mac. SalePaste has no network connectivity and does not use analytics, tracking, or third-party services of any kind.

Clipboard contents are read only to detect and adjust numeric prices, and the result is written back to your local clipboard. Nothing is ever sent off your device.

